[SPEAKER_00] Ali ništa, što će ja.

818
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ono ignoriram, k'o da, k'o da ja ne znam.

819
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Žena ne zna. I odu djeca, trču.

820
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon par minuta, čujem da Marija kaže:

821
00:40:49,000 --> 00:40:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Joj, ti si se ukakio, imate mijenjati."

822
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ona nema pojma da sam ja to osjetio, da sam ja znao.

823
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mijenja ona maloga i idemo dalje.

824
00:40:58,000 --> 00:41:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tada sam shvatio da je to kontrasepcija.

825
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam mogao nešto dati od sebe,

826
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] a sam tada bio ljen,

827
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam bio na poslu, o, o, ono, neću ja.

828
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tada sam shvatio što je kontrasepcija.

829
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] A želim to podijeliti jer to je jako bitno.

830
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Netko od vas možda nije u braku, netko je.

831
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali možete vježbat sada.

832
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to je naš poziv.

833
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] I vrlo je bitno.

834
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad me ljudi pitaju za ovu odluku za Hrvatsku,

835
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] se doselit ili se vratit,

836
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] je li to teška odluka?

837
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svima ja kažem da je, teška je odluka.

838
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali iskreno nije.

839
00:41:58,000 --> 00:42:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najteža odluka u mom životu

840
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] je ono što smo ja i moje supruga, što je jako teško,

841
00:42:13,000 --> 00:42:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] smo rekli životu da.

842
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najteža odluka.

843
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to nije ono bilo jednom da ćemo biti otvorenom životu.

844
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nego to je odluka što je pala ne znam koliko puta,

845
00:42:25,000 --> 00:42:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] sebi moram pa milijon puta reći.

846
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najteža odluka.

847
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ova odluka za Hrvatsku niti blizu.

848
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači kako je izgledalo to za Hrvatsku?

849
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:39,000
