850
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju sam radio za Sidnjsku nadbiskupiju

851
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] zaotvoreno kažem, plaća u crkvi nisu neke visoke plaće.

852
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam ja ušao radi u katoličku školu,

853
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] meni se moja plaća smanjala na 30% od ono što sam zarađivo.

854
00:42:55,000 --> 00:43:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znao sam da sam imao poziv da trebam nešto učiniti

855
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:03,000
