943
00:46:16,000 --> 00:46:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I u oči mise, u oči blagdana, 12.6.2023.

944
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Točno znam.

945
00:46:24,000 --> 00:46:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Za vrijeme mise.

946
00:46:26,000 --> 00:46:28,000
