952
00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja šutim.

953
00:46:52,000 --> 00:46:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon pola minute sam osjetio toplinu i mir.

954
00:46:58,000 --> 00:47:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tada sam znao da ću se doselit ili vratit u Hrvatsku.

955
00:47:05,000 --> 00:47:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Točno sam znao.

956
00:47:07,000 --> 00:47:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] I znači taj mir i toplina je još uvijek sa mnom.

957
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad me ljudi pitaju kako je u Hrvatskoj, pa pre dobro, pre lijepo.

958
00:47:17,000 --> 00:47:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa od automehaničara do Mupa, strukovna škola, ravnateljica Vamo, osnovna škola, Vrtić.

959
00:47:28,000 --> 00:47:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma fizioterap Marko, legenda, Ana, Marija, iskočio mi disk.

960
00:47:33,000 --> 00:47:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Di got idem, ma pre dobro.

961
00:47:37,000 --> 00:47:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije normalno.

962
00:47:39,000 --> 00:47:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Volim tu riječ, nije normalno.

963
00:47:42,000 --> 00:47:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nisam normalan.

964
00:47:44,000 --> 00:47:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se ona sjećam u sidan, nisam normalan.

965
00:47:47,000 --> 00:47:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] I znaš, i dečki igraju nogomet.

966
00:47:49,000 --> 00:47:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja nakon sezona, jer smo mi došli na pologodinu, ja zovem njega i kažem treneru:

967
00:47:55,000 --> 00:47:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam što ste nas primjeli.

968
00:47:58,000 --> 00:48:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko što nema problemi? Pa što? Vi ste normalni.

969
00:48:01,000 --> 00:48:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rekle: Ne, ne, ne znaš.

970
00:48:06,000 --> 00:48:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam.

971
00:48:08,000 --> 00:48:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, kome sam se god zafalio, kažem:

972
00:48:12,000 --> 00:48:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dobro, ti si normalan, normalan.

973
00:48:15,000 --> 00:48:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što? Zašto ne bi?

974
00:48:17,000 --> 00:48:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I znači, tu smo godinu dana.

975
00:48:21,000 --> 00:48:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Djeca idu u školu.

976
00:48:23,000 --> 00:48:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki ima svoj neki put.

977
00:48:26,000 --> 00:48:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali što je prije toga bilo?

978
00:48:30,000 --> 00:48:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ja sam bio u Australiji godinu dana.

979
00:48:33,000 --> 00:48:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Skoro godinu i pol dana.

980
00:48:36,000 --> 00:48:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto manje.

981
00:48:38,000 --> 00:48:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odkad je ta odluka pala.

982
00:48:42,000 --> 00:48:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ja sam trebao prvi mjesec isplakat ovo ono, da prođu emocije.

983
00:48:48,000 --> 00:48:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I naravno, Bog mi je dao taj mir.

984
00:48:52,000 --> 00:48:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako kad sam ja to podijelio dalje sa roditeljima, sa obiteljima, oni su bili u šoku.

985
00:48:58,000 --> 00:49:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam već prošao taj šok, a ono se razmišljam, joj moram se vratiti.

986
00:49:02,000 --> 00:49:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sjećam se, prošlo neko vrijeme i ono kao moji roditelj stvarno.

987
00:49:09,000 --> 00:49:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao: "Da, to je to."

988
00:49:11,000 --> 00:49:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda smo prodali kuću.

989
00:49:14,000 --> 00:49:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam tako izašao, ja sam tako volio, ajmo ovi ljudi ko me znaju, i uložio sam kuću.

990
00:49:22,000 --> 00:49:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako mi je bilo lijepo tamo, tako drago.

991
00:49:25,000 --> 00:49:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sam samo jedan dan otišao do agencije i kažem: "Prodajem."

992
00:49:29,000 --> 00:49:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] I prodali.

993
00:49:31,000 --> 00:49:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prodaje auto, dao odkaz.

994
00:49:34,000 --> 00:49:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sve sam ja pomalo to očistio.

995
00:49:37,000 --> 00:49:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tada su ljudi oko mene bili: "Vi stvarno idete?"

996
00:49:41,000 --> 00:49:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao: "Da."

997
00:49:43,000 --> 00:49:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] I moj otec mene pita: "Sine, zašto me ostavljaš?"

998
00:49:51,000 --> 00:49:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja rekao: "Tata, ja ne znam."

999
00:49:55,000 --> 00:49:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tata je 47. godišće.

1000
00:49:58,000 --> 00:50:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne znam, ali znam preko zagovora svetog Antuna

1001
00:50:04,000 --> 00:50:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] da me ohrabrio i da moram ići.

1002
00:50:08,000 --> 00:50:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da ti ja sada točno kažem zašto, ne znam.

1003
00:50:13,000 --> 00:50:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je razlog.

1004
00:50:17,000 --> 00:50:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda on meni kaže: "U redu."

1005
00:50:21,000 --> 00:50:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Jel ti znaš kad sam ja odlazio iz svoga sela za Australiju?"

1006
00:50:26,000 --> 00:50:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja rekao: "Ne znam."

1007
00:50:27,000 --> 00:50:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Da svetog Antuna."

1008
00:50:29,000 --> 00:50:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao: "Stvarno."

1009
00:50:34,000 --> 00:50:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda moja mama dođe i kaže: "Sine, jel ti znaš kad sam ja odlazio iz Australije?"

1010
00:50:39,000 --> 00:50:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] 73.

1011
00:50:41,000 --> 00:50:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao: "Ne znam."

1012
00:50:43,000 --> 00:50:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isto.

1013
00:50:45,000 --> 00:50:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Za svetog Antuna.

1014
00:50:49,000 --> 00:51:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] I gdje smo mi došli u crkvu svetog Antuna u Sidniju, tamo su se moji vjenčali, tamo sam ja vjenčao, tamo se moja supruga krstila, ja, moja djeca.

1015
00:51:01,000 --> 00:51:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tada mi je sveti Antuna, ne da sam ga ignorirao, više sam malo zavolio svetog Josipa u ovih zadnjih 5-6 godina, a sveti Antuna ne da.

1016
00:51:17,000 --> 00:51:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ovaj, tako da, sad što se dogodilo, moji roditelji su prodali svoju kuću i dolazu, evo, na godinu, isto nakon 50, tata nakon 50 i 6 godina se vraća u hrvatsku domovinu.

1017
00:51:37,000 --> 00:51:39,000
[UNKNOWN] Aplauz.

1018
00:51:39,000 --> 00:51:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što je bitno tu? Znači, na engleskom mi kažemo discernment, ja sam to...

1019
00:51:59,000 --> 00:52:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Razlučivanje.

1020
00:52:02,000 --> 00:52:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Razlučivanje. Bravo.

1021
00:52:04,000 --> 00:52:18,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo bi podijelio s vama.

1022
00:52:18,099 --> 00:52:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, znate sada da ljubav nije osjećaj i znate da opros nije osjećaj.

1023
00:52:26,380 --> 00:52:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] i da ljubav i opraštaj su odluka.

1024
00:52:32,380 --> 00:52:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav je žrtva, ljubav je činiti dobro drugima.

1025
00:52:37,380 --> 00:52:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] I kad to činiš, to ne znači da to uvijek osjeća dobro, iako je dobro.

1026
00:52:48,380 --> 00:52:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je primjer sa djecom.

1027
00:52:50,380 --> 00:52:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] Djeta ti povraća dva ujutro, ja se tebi da ustati i očisti to?

1028
00:52:56,380 --> 00:53:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ali zašto činiš? Jer i voliš, ljubiš. To je odluka.

1029
00:53:00,380 --> 00:53:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ništa u našem svijetu ne funkcionira na osjećaj.

1030
00:53:06,380 --> 00:53:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa, jer bi propala odmah.

1031
00:53:09,380 --> 00:53:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] I tako je o duhovnom životu.

1032
00:53:12,380 --> 00:53:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovo, kako prepoznati Božji glas i vršiti njegovu volju, što je tu bitno?

1033
00:53:21,380 --> 00:53:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se molite na tu nakanu, Bože, što želiš od mene?

1034
00:53:28,380 --> 00:53:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] Da ste skroz otvoreni.

1035
00:53:30,380 --> 00:53:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] Bez granica.

1036
00:53:33,380 --> 00:53:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kako onda se uvježbat?

1037
00:53:37,380 --> 00:53:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ja to ne mogu. Ja moram kontrolirat.

1038
00:53:41,380 --> 00:53:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, evo, da ću...

1039
00:53:45,380 --> 00:53:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, kratku priču, znači, prije nego što smo odlazili.

1040
00:53:49,380 --> 00:53:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam znao što ću ja ovdje radit, samo sam znao...

1041
00:53:53,380 --> 00:53:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako sam ja i prijateljima rekao.

1042
00:53:55,380 --> 00:53:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao, slušaj.

1043
00:53:56,380 --> 00:53:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, kad hoda sa curom

1044
00:53:58,380 --> 00:54:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] i mi na engleskom kažemo "pop the question".

1045
00:54:02,380 --> 00:54:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kužite: "Will you marry me?"

1046
00:54:06,380 --> 00:54:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Hoćete me oženiti?"

1047
00:54:07,380 --> 00:54:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi tako kaže? Oženiti?

1048
00:54:09,380 --> 00:54:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] Udat. Ona će se uda i ja će se ženiti.

1049
00:54:11,380 --> 00:54:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

1050
00:54:12,380 --> 00:54:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] I ona kaže: "Da".

1051
00:54:13,380 --> 00:54:18,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, sada vas u tom trenutku neko pita:

1052
00:54:18,380 --> 00:54:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Gi ćete živit?"

1053
00:54:20,380 --> 00:54:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Koliko će ti djeca imat?"

1054
00:54:21,380 --> 00:54:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Žto će te radi?"

1055
00:54:23,380 --> 00:54:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Žto će bit za godinu dana?"

1056
00:54:24,380 --> 00:54:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Dvi godine?"

1057
00:54:25,380 --> 00:54:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Pet godina?"

1058
00:54:26,380 --> 00:54:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ili ne i to?"

1059
00:54:27,380 --> 00:54:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Gdje ćete se vjenčat?"

1060
00:54:29,380 --> 00:54:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Koji datum?"

1061
00:54:30,380 --> 00:54:31,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Kako će bit?"

1062
00:54:31,380 --> 00:54:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Hoće li bit bend?"

1063
00:54:32,380 --> 00:54:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ko će svirat?"

1064
00:54:33,380 --> 00:54:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] Pa vi bi rekli: "Slušajte, ja ne znam, tek sam je pito."

1065
00:54:37,380 --> 00:54:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] I to se meni dogodilo u oči svetog Antuna.

1066
00:54:42,380 --> 00:54:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je Bog bredao.

1067
00:54:44,380 --> 00:54:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako jasno i glasno.

1068
00:54:47,380 --> 00:54:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] I na mene je bilo isto da pitaš suru da kaže da ili ne.

1069
00:54:52,380 --> 00:54:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] I kad sam ja rekao da i ljudi su meni počeli pitao:

1070
00:54:55,380 --> 00:54:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ali Ivica, što ćeš radi?"

1071
00:54:56,380 --> 00:54:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Nemam pojma."

1072
00:54:57,380 --> 00:54:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Kako ne znaš?

1073
00:54:58,380 --> 00:55:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Dje ću djeca ići u školu?"

1074
00:55:00,380 --> 00:55:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne znam."

1075
00:55:01,380 --> 00:55:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Dje ćeš živit?"

1076
00:55:02,380 --> 00:55:04,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne znam."

1077
00:55:05,380 --> 00:55:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] "I što je bilo?"

1078
00:55:06,380 --> 00:55:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ja sam počeo njuškat."

1079
00:55:07,380 --> 00:55:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne previše."

1080
00:55:08,380 --> 00:55:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ali teško naći."

1081
00:55:10,380 --> 00:55:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Nas je devetoro."

1082
00:55:11,380 --> 00:55:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam got rekao:

1083
00:55:12,380 --> 00:55:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Hej, ja ono, na veče u Sidniju jer ovdje je onda po danu."

1084
00:55:16,380 --> 00:55:18,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Nas je devetoro."

1085
00:55:18,380 --> 00:55:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa jeste radnici."

1086
00:55:19,380 --> 00:55:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Jesam."

1087
00:55:20,380 --> 00:55:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Jesam."

1088
00:55:21,380 --> 00:55:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Jes nisu tijeli dat."

1089
00:55:22,380 --> 00:55:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Znaš, je rekao:

1090
00:55:23,380 --> 00:55:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne, to sam ja, supruga i sedmoro djece."

1091
00:55:26,380 --> 00:55:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne, ne možemo iznajmit, jer samo možemo da radnicima."

1092
00:55:29,380 --> 00:55:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Jes rekao:

1093
00:55:30,380 --> 00:55:31,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Dobro, onda smo radnici."

1094
00:55:31,380 --> 00:55:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne, ne, ne."

1095
00:55:32,380 --> 00:55:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] "I ništa od toga."

1096
00:55:35,380 --> 00:55:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Znači, recimo, nakon edeljne misle, ljudi me pitaju često:

1097
00:55:41,380 --> 00:55:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Gi ćete? Što ćete?"

1098
00:55:42,380 --> 00:55:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Još tri mjeseca."

1099
00:55:43,380 --> 00:55:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Jes rekao:

1100
00:55:44,380 --> 00:55:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne znam."

1101
00:55:45,380 --> 00:55:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Idemo u okolicu Zagreba, vjerovatno."

1102
00:55:47,380 --> 00:55:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] "A nemaš gdje?"

1103
00:55:49,380 --> 00:55:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Jes rekao:

1104
00:55:50,380 --> 00:55:50,380
[UNKNOWN] "Ne."

1105
00:55:50,380 --> 00:55:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ja pošaljem poruku sjestični i nekim prijateljima."

1106
00:55:54,380 --> 00:55:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Jes rekao:

1107
00:55:55,380 --> 00:55:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Da, ako nešto nađete, treba nam, dolazimo u 11. mjesecu."

1108
00:55:58,380 --> 00:56:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Nije baš toplo."

1109
00:56:01,380 --> 00:56:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] I znači, idemo mi leč.

1110
00:56:05,380 --> 00:56:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, za dva mjeseca mi odlazimo.

1111
00:56:08,380 --> 00:56:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam smještaj, ništa.

1112
00:56:12,380 --> 00:56:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa nismo organizirali, nikoga kontaktirali.

1113
00:56:15,380 --> 00:56:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem Marije:

1114
00:56:16,380 --> 00:56:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Slušaj, večerez ću ja ovo riješiti."

1115
00:56:19,380 --> 00:56:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] Imao sam, došlo mi je čisto, znam da ću riješiti.

1116
00:56:21,380 --> 00:56:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nisam znao, ali...

1117
00:56:24,380 --> 00:56:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] Došlo je.

1118
00:56:26,380 --> 00:56:28,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je ona leč.

1119
00:56:28,380 --> 00:56:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] I ja, osim Budan, tipkam.

1120
00:56:32,380 --> 00:56:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, odgovori.

1121
00:56:34,380 --> 00:56:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] Muž od cestične:

1122
00:56:36,380 --> 00:56:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Evo, nama ovaj susjed renovira, švabo."

1123
00:56:39,380 --> 00:56:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] Misli, naš čovjek, švabo.

1124
00:56:42,380 --> 00:56:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] Oće li prodati, oće li u najam, nemam pojma.

1125
00:56:46,380 --> 00:56:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ja u Hrvatskoj nemam ništa.

1126
00:56:48,380 --> 00:56:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ni kuću, zemljište, ništa.

1127
00:56:50,380 --> 00:56:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] I znači, on kaže:

1128
00:56:52,380 --> 00:56:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Da, ide kuća u najam."

1129
00:56:54,380 --> 00:56:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja rekao: "Super, ne mogu ja da ovdje kupi kuću.

1130
00:56:56,380 --> 00:56:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bi kupio auto, kamo li kuću."

1131
00:56:59,380 --> 00:57:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] I znači, snima mi on.

1132
00:57:01,380 --> 00:57:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] I meni to riješeno.

1133
00:57:03,380 --> 00:57:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja njemu kažem: "Riješeno."

1134
00:57:06,380 --> 00:57:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja rekao: "Daj ti broj od vlasnika."

1135
00:57:09,380 --> 00:57:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] I Marija se ustane ujutro.

1136
00:57:11,380 --> 00:57:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja malo spavo, jako zec, čekam da se...

1137
00:57:14,380 --> 00:57:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] I gleda ona u mene i rekao: "Što je?"

1138
00:57:17,380 --> 00:57:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao: "Riješeno, imamo smještaj."

1139
00:57:20,380 --> 00:57:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno, ja poglažem te dvi snimke.

1140
00:57:22,380 --> 00:57:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi stvarno...

1141
00:57:23,380 --> 00:57:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao: "Riješio sam, a nisam još sa vlasnikom,

1142
00:57:26,380 --> 00:57:28,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali znam da je riješeno."

1143
00:57:28,380 --> 00:57:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] I znači, meni...

1144
00:57:30,380 --> 00:57:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] Franjo, Bog te blagoslovio.

1145
00:57:32,380 --> 00:57:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] Koji je to čovjek?

1146
00:57:34,380 --> 00:57:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, naš u Australiji je to jeno biznes,

1147
00:57:37,380 --> 00:57:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] sajmo, kuća najam.

1148
00:57:40,380 --> 00:57:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] A čovjek je tijelo mene upoznat.

1149
00:57:42,380 --> 00:57:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao: "Ja sebi moram biti iskren.

1150
00:57:45,380 --> 00:57:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] Neću reći da imam četvrlo djece,

1151
00:57:47,380 --> 00:57:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] da uguram još troje, da se on ne uplaši."

1152
00:57:49,380 --> 00:57:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Nas je voliko."

1153
00:57:51,380 --> 00:57:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] A tu su samo tri spaveće,

1154
00:57:53,380 --> 00:57:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] sobe i gaderobo.

1155
00:57:54,380 --> 00:57:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao: "U gaderobu mogu nas njih troje, ne brini."

1156
00:57:57,380 --> 00:58:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] I tako...

1157
00:58:01,380 --> 00:58:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] A Franjo mene pita:

1158
00:58:03,380 --> 00:58:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Pa zašto? Kako?

1159
00:58:05,380 --> 00:58:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja njemu isto otvorno srcu sve kažem."

1160
00:58:07,380 --> 00:58:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže: "Dobro, dogovoreno."

1161
00:58:09,380 --> 00:58:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao: "Čovjek će se uplašit."

1162
00:58:13,380 --> 00:58:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] Još on kaže: "Ajmo vidi okoli."

1163
00:58:15,380 --> 00:58:18,380
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao: "Daj, vidit ćeš brado, ljudi će se uplašit."

1164
00:58:18,380 --> 00:58:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] "Ali nije, evo."

1165
00:58:20,380 --> 00:58:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] I tako da dva mjeseca, točno dva mjeseca, ja u sve toj nedlji gdje živimo sada, sam bio jednom, možda na sat ili sat vremena.

1166
00:58:30,380 --> 00:58:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jednom.

1167
00:58:32,380 --> 00:58:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] I došao ja živit.

1168
00:58:34,380 --> 00:58:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] I ljudi pitaju kako je.

1169
00:58:35,380 --> 00:58:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] Pre dobro.

1170
00:58:36,380 --> 00:58:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] Susjedi, najbolji susjedi, Ivek, Martina, ovdje ja ne bravim svi, su super.

1171
00:58:42,380 --> 00:58:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] Odlično.

1172
00:58:43,380 --> 00:58:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] Blagoslov, blagoslov gdje smo došli.

1173
00:58:45,380 --> 00:58:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] Što će ja raditi?

1174
00:58:46,380 --> 00:58:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi me pitaju kako radiš.

1175
00:58:48,380 --> 00:58:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] Otvorio sam firmu.

1176
00:58:50,380 --> 00:58:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] Zove se Berala.

1177
00:58:52,380 --> 00:58:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, gdje sam ja živio 47 godina.

1178
00:58:55,380 --> 00:58:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] Firma se zove, to naselje se zove Berala.

1179
00:58:59,380 --> 00:59:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je firma se zove.

1180
00:59:02,380 --> 00:59:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] Čisto zbog toga.

1181
00:59:03,380 --> 00:59:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] I ušao sam u građevini i imam divni prijatelji preko rođaka koji su me uputili.

1182
00:59:10,380 --> 00:59:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] I ljudi kaže, ti si o tim bavio?

1183
00:59:12,380 --> 00:59:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao nikada u životu.

1184
00:59:14,380 --> 00:59:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] A meni je to takav izazov.

1185
00:59:17,380 --> 00:59:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] Učim, gledam ko malo dite.

1186
00:59:19,380 --> 00:59:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je dobro.

1187
00:59:20,380 --> 00:59:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte se bojati.

1188
00:59:22,380 --> 00:59:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] Vi to možda znate.

1189
00:59:24,380 --> 00:59:28,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam uvijek mislio da...

1190
00:59:28,380 --> 00:59:31,380
[SPEAKER_00] Suprutnost vjere...

1191
00:59:31,380 --> 00:59:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] Suprutnost...

1192
00:59:32,380 --> 00:59:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu ni izgovoriti.

1193
00:59:34,380 --> 00:59:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] Da...

1194
00:59:36,380 --> 00:59:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam mislio da je nevjera.

1195
00:59:39,380 --> 00:59:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ako čovjek ima vjeru, ima vjeru.

1196
00:59:41,380 --> 00:59:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ako čovjek nema vjeru, znači atijest ili ništa ne vjeruje.

1197
00:59:46,380 --> 00:59:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nije, nego je strah.

1198
00:59:49,380 --> 00:59:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] Zato nemojte se bojati.

1199
00:59:52,380 --> 00:59:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ne treba imati strah.

1200
00:59:54,380 --> 00:59:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] Strah nije od Boga.

1201
00:59:56,380 --> 00:59:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] Treba imati vjeru.

1202
01:00:04,380 --> 01:00:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] Nadu.

1203
01:00:05,380 --> 01:00:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] A što najviše.

1204
01:00:07,380 --> 01:00:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav.

1205
01:00:09,380 --> 01:00:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] Charity.

1206
01:00:11,380 --> 01:00:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] Karitas.

1207
01:00:12,380 --> 01:00:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] I vi, svi, odanas.

1208
01:00:15,380 --> 01:00:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] Iako niste u braku, razmišljajte o tome što sam kratko rekao za kontrasepciju.

1209
01:00:24,380 --> 01:00:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] Da je kad je Isus dao sve od sebe.

1210
01:00:27,380 --> 01:00:31,380
[SPEAKER_00] Nije rekao da ne dam lijevu ruku, nego dao je sve od sebe.

1211
01:00:31,380 --> 01:00:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tako muškarcima.

1212
01:00:33,380 --> 01:00:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je pelana se mali ukakio, mijenjajte pelenu.

1213
01:00:38,380 --> 01:00:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] Svi možete vježbat to.

1214
01:00:41,380 --> 01:00:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ljudi misle, nisam u braku, kako to mogu vježbat?

1215
01:00:45,380 --> 01:00:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] Nego činite.

1216
01:00:47,380 --> 01:00:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav je odluka.

1217
01:00:48,380 --> 01:00:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav su dijela.

1218
01:00:50,380 --> 01:00:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] I ljubav je Bog prvi.

1219
01:00:53,380 --> 01:00:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] Drugi, susjed su drugi i uvijek si ti treći.

1220
01:00:57,380 --> 01:01:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, tako mijenjamo sebe i mijenjamo svijet.

